              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                我对生命说：&quot;我要听死亡说话。&quot; 生命把她的声音提高一点说：&quot;现在你听到他说话了。&quot; 当你解答了生命的一切奥秘，你就渴望死亡，因为它不过是生命的另一个 奥秘。 生与死是勇敢的两种最高贵的表现。——纪伯伦<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>I said to Life, &quot;I would hear Death speak.&quot;And Life raised her voice a little higher and said, &quot;You hear him now.&quot; When you have solved all the mysteries of life you long for death, for it is but another mystery of life. Birth and death are the two noblest expressions of bravery.

