              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                “我们的头脑是一块海绵；我们的心是一道溪流。 然而我们大多宁愿吸收而不肯奔流，这不是很奇怪吗？ Our mind is a sponge; our heart is a stream. Is it not strange that most of us choose sucking rather than running?”<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>“灵感总是歌唱；灵感从不解释。 Inspiration will always sing; inspiration will never explain.”
